\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces In the Coin Game, two agents, `red' and `blue', get 1 point for picking up any coin. However, the `red agent' loses 2 points when the `blue agent' picks up a red coin and vice versa. Effectively, this is a world with an embedded social dilemma where cooperation and defection are temporally extended.\relax }}{6}{figure.caption.9}}
\newlabel{fig:fig_coin_game}{{3}{6}{In the Coin Game, two agents, `red' and `blue', get 1 point for picking up any coin. However, the `red agent' loses 2 points when the `blue agent' picks up a red coin and vice versa. Effectively, this is a world with an embedded social dilemma where cooperation and defection are temporally extended.\relax }{figure.caption.9}{}}
\newlabel{fig:fig_coin_game@cref}{{[figure][3][]3}{6}}
